cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.CR

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with crowd counting in the wild using synthetic data and proposes methods to improve the performance of crowd counting models. 
2. cs.LG (Machine Learning) is also likely as the paper proposes two schemes that exploit synthetic data to boost the performance of crowd counting models. 
3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with developing a data collector and labeler that can generate synthetic crowd scenes and annotate them without any manpower. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) is also possible as the paper deals with crowd scenes in videos and proposes methods to count the number of people in them. 
5. cs.CR (Cryptography and Security) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions the applications of crowd counting in video surveillance and public security.
